    "Subjects could then determine whether to opt-in or opt-out of the study over the course of the next four weeks (noting that we deemed nonresponse to the recruitment emails as opting out of the study).",
    "For additional information about study protocols, please see Methods for a copy of the recruitment emails sent out in Phase 2.",
    "Please also visit the following Open Science Framework (OSF) Web Page https:// osf.",
    "io/ jn8m7/ for copies of all Phase 4 treatment materials.",
    "Finally, note that we carried out all Phase 2 and Phase 4 randomization procedures using the random integer generation command runiformint in Stata 15."
